      "html": "<link data-kid=\"1\" data-name=\"Tabler icon webfont stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tabler/icons-webfont/tabler-icons.min.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n<style data-kid=\"0\">\n  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Outfit:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap');\n  \n  .glass-panel {\n    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75);\n    backdrop-filter: blur(24px) saturate(120%);\n    -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(24px) saturate(120%);\n    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);\n  }\n\n  .input-glow:focus {\n    outline: none;\n    border-color: #2563EB;\n    box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.15);\n  }\n\n  .ripple-btn {\n    position: relative;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    transition: all 0.3s ease;\n  }\n  .ripple-btn:hover {\n    transform: translateY(-2px);\n    box-shadow: 0 10px 20px -10px rgba(37, 99, 235, 0.5);\n  }\n  \n  .animate-float {\n    animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;\n  }\n\n  @keyframes float {\n    0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px); }\n    50% { transform: translateY(-20px); }\n  }\n\n  @keyframes marquee {\n    0% { transform: translateX(0); }\n    100% { transform: translateX(-50%); }\n  }\n\n  .dark-map-inset {\n    background: #0F172A;\n    background-image: radial-gradient(circle at 2px 2px, rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1) 1px, transparent 0);\n    background-size: 24px 24px;\n  }\n\n  .blob-purple { background: #8B5CF6; }\n  .blob-emerald { background: #10B981; }\n</style>\n<div class=\"relative w-full bg-[#F8FAFC] font-['Outfit'] overflow-x-hidden text-[#0F172A]\" data-kid=\"2\" data-name=\"page layout wrapper\">\n\n<div class=\"absolute top-[-10%] left-[-5%] w-[800px] h-[800px] blob-purple/10 rounded-full blur-[120px]\" data-kid=\"2-1\" data-name=\"purple background blob\"></div>\n<div class=\"absolute top-[40%] right-[-10%] w-[900px] h-[900px] blob-emerald/10 rounded-full blur-[140px]\" data-kid=\"2-2\" data-name=\"emerald background blob\"></div>\n<div class=\"absolute bottom-[-10%] left-[20%] w-[700px] h-[700px] blob-purple/10 rounded-full blur-[120px]\" data-kid=\"2-3\" data-name=\"purple background blob\"></div>\n\n<header class=\"fixed top-0 left-0 right-0 z-50 px-8 py-6 pointer-events-none\" data-kid=\"2-4\" data-name=\"fixed navigation header\">\n<nav class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto h-20 glass-panel rounded-full px-8 flex items-center shadow-2xl pointer-events-auto\" data-kid=\"2-4-1\" data-name=\"glass navigation panel\">\n<div class=\"flex items-center gap-3 mr-auto\" data-kid=\"2-4-1-1\" data-name=\"brand logo and name container\">\n<div class=\"w-10 h-10 bg-blue-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-white shadow-lg shadow-blue-600/20\" data-kid=\"2-4-1-1-1\" data-name=\"logo icon background box\">\n<i class=\"ti ti-truck text-2xl\" data-kid=\"2-4-1-1-1-1\" data-name=\"truck icon\"></i>\n</div>\n<span class=\"text-2xl font-black tracking-tight\" data-kid=\"2-4-1-1-2\" data-name=\"brand name text\">Transit<span class=\"text-blue-600\" data-kid=\"2-4-1-1-2-1\" data-name=\"brand name suffix text\">Ops</span></span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"hidden md:flex items-center gap-10 text-sm font-bold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-widest px-12\" data-kid=\"2-4-1-2\" data-name=\"navigation menu links\">\n<a class=\"hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors\" data-kid=\"2-4-1-2-1\" data-name=\"platform link\" href=\"#\">Platform</a>\n<a class=\"hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors\" data-kid=\"2-4-1-2-2\" data-name=\"solutions link\" href=\"#\">Solutions</a>\n<a class=\"hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors\" data-kid=\"2-4-1-2-3\" data-name=\"fleet intelligence link\" href=\"#\">Fleet Intelligence</a>\n<a class=\"hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors\" data-kid=\"2-4-1-2-4\" data-name=\"pricing link\" href=\"#\">Pricing</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"ml-auto flex items-center gap-4\" data-kid=\"2-4-1-3\" data-name=\"request demo button container\">\n<button class=\"px-8 py-3 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full text-sm font-bold ripple-btn shadow-lg shadow-blue-600/30\" data-kid=\"2-4-1-3-1\" data-name=\"request demo button\">\n          Request Demo\n        </button>\n</div>\n</nav>\n</header>\n\n<section class=\"relative pt-48 pb-32 px-8\" data-kid=\"2-5\" data-name=\"hero section\">\n<div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto flex flex-col items-center text-center\" data-kid=\"2-5-1\" data-name=\"hero content container\">\n<div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-blue-50 text-blue-600 rounded-full text-[10px] font-black uppercase tracking-widest mb-8 border border-blue-100\" data-kid=\"2-5-1-1\" data-name=\"hero status badge\">\n<span class=\"w-1.5 h-1.5 bg-blue-600 rounded-full animate-pulse\" data-kid=\"2-5-1-1-1\" data-name=\"pulsing status dot\"></span>\n        Operational Excellence Realized\n      </div>\n<h1 class=\"text-7xl md:text-8xl font-black leading-[0.95] tracking-tight mb-8 max-w-4xl\" data-kid=\"2-5-1-2\" data-name=\"hero headline text\">\n        Command Your Fleet <br data-kid=\"2-5-1-2-1\" data-name=\"headline line break\"> with <span class=\"text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-600 to-indigo-600\" data-kid=\"2-5-1-2-2\" data-name=\"hero headline highlighted text\">Absolute Precision.</span>\n</h1>\n<p class=\"text-xl text-gray-500 max-w-2xl mb-12\" data-kid=\"2-5-1-3\" data-name=\"hero subheadline text\">\n        Digitize your entire logistics lifecycle. From AI-driven dispatching to real-time driver safety monitoring—one command center, total visibility.\n      </p>\n\n<div class=\"relative w-full max-w-5xl mt-12 group\" data-kid=\"2-5-1-4\" data-name=\"hero interactive visual container\">\n\n<div class=\"absolute inset-0 dark-map-inset rounded-[4rem] opacity-20 transform scale-95 group-hover:scale-100 transition-transform duration-700\" data-kid=\"2-5-1-4-1\" data-name=\"dashboard grid backdrop\"></div>\n\n<div class=\"relative z-10 py-20 flex justify-center\" data-kid=\"2-5-1-4-2\" data-name=\"central truck image wrapper\">\n<img alt=\"Modern electric delivery truck\" class=\"w-full max-w-3xl animate-float drop-shadow-[0_35px_35px_rgba(0,0,0,0.15)]\" data-kid=\"2-5-1-4-2-1\" data-name=\"electric truck image\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1732193933813-4da17265a36c?auto=format&amp;w=1200&amp;q=80&amp;fit=crop\">\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"absolute top-[20%] left-[-5%] glass-panel p-6 rounded-3xl shadow-2xl max-w-[240px] text-left animate-float\" data-kid=\"2-5-1-4-3\" data-name=\"fleet safety score card\" style=\"animation-delay: -1s;\">\n<div class=\"flex items-center justify-between mb-4\" data-kid=\"2-5-1-4-3-1\" data-name=\"card header\">\n<i class=\"ti ti-shield-check text-blue-600 text-2xl\" data-kid=\"2-5-1-4-3-1-1\" data-name=\"shield icon\"></i>\n<span class=\"text-[10px] font-black text-blue-600 bg-blue-50 px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full\" data-kid=\"2-5-1-4-3-1-2\" data-name=\"live status badge\">LIVE</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"text-4xl font-black mb-1\" data-kid=\"2-5-1-4-3-2\" data-name=\"safety score text\">94.2</div>\n<div class=\"text-[10px] font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest\" data-kid=\"2-5-1-4-3-3\" data-name=\"safety score label\">Fleet Safety Score</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"absolute bottom-[30%] right-[-5%] glass-panel p-6 rounded-3xl shadow-2xl max-w-[240px] text-left animate-float\" data-kid=\"2-5-1-4-4\" data-name=\"active trips card\" style=\"animation-delay: -3s;\">\n<div class=\"flex items-center justify-center border-4 border-blue-100 w-16 h-16 rounded-full mb-4 relative\" data-kid=\"2-5-1-4-4-1\" data-name=\"progress ring wrapper\">\n<i class=\"ti ti-activity text-blue-600\" data-kid=\"2-5-1-4-4-1-1\" data-name=\"activity icon\"></i>\n<svg class=\"absolute inset-0 w-full h-full -rotate-90\" data-kid=\"2-5-1-4-4-1-2\" data-name=\"progress svg\">\n<circle cx=\"32\" cy=\"32\" fill=\"transparent\" r=\"28\" stroke=\"#2563EB\" stroke-dasharray=\"175.9\" stroke-dashoffset=\"35\" stroke-width=\"4\" data-kid=\"3\"></circle>\n</svg>\n</div>\n<div class=\"text-3xl font-black mb-1 text-blue-600\" data-kid=\"2-5-1-4-4-2\" data-name=\"active trips count text\">1,204</div>\n<div class=\"text-[10px] font-bold text-gray-400 uppercase tracking-widest\" data-kid=\"2-5-1-4-4-3\" data-name=\"active trips label\">Active Trips Today</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</section>\n\n<section class=\"py-24 px-8 bg-white/30 backdrop-blur-md\" data-kid=\"2-6\" data-name=\"features section\">\n<div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto\" data-kid=\"2-6-1\" data-name=\"features container\">\n<div class=\"text-center mb-20\" data-kid=\"2-6-1-1\" data-name=\"section header group\">\n<h2 class=\"text-4xl font-black mb-4\" data-kid=\"2-6-1-1-1\" data-name=\"section title\">Enterprise-Grade Fleet Control</h2>\n<p class=\"text-gray-500\" data-kid=\"2-6-1-1-2\" data-name=\"section description\">Built for scale, designed for simplicity.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8\" data-kid=\"2-6-1-2\" data-name=\"features grid\">\n\n<div class=\"glass-panel rounded-[3rem] p-10 flex flex-col hover:border-amber-400/50 transition-colors group\" data-kid=\"2-6-1-2-1\" data-name=\"unified registry card\">\n<div class=\"w-16 h-16 bg-amber-50 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-amber-500 mb-8 border border-amber-100 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform\" data-kid=\"2-6-1-2-1-1\" data-name=\"archive icon box\">\n<i class=\"ti ti-archive text-3xl\" data-kid=\"2-6-1-2-1-1-1\" data-name=\"archive icon\"></i>\n</div>\n<h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold mb-4\" data-kid=\"2-6-1-2-1-2\" data-name=\"feature title\">Unified Registry</h3>\n<p class=\"text-gray-500 mb-8 leading-relaxed\" data-kid=\"2-6-1-2-1-3\" data-name=\"feature description\">Centralize vehicle lifecycle management. Track odometer, maintenance logs, and ROI in one granular view.</p>\n<div class=\"mt-auto p-4 bg-amber-50 rounded-2xl border border-amber-100\" data-kid=\"2-6-1-2-1-4\" data-name=\"fuel efficiency indicator container\">\n<div class=\"flex i